content: Would not auto rotate. Not good game play.
Clean UI, ad-free after purchase without needing to pay a recurring subscription.

I played this for a few mins, but the flashing cards got very annoying when I was using it as a way to relax. Otherwise it is a fine game, just I play to fall asleep and having a card flash constantly didn't help in my end goal.
Really enjoy playing. A simple game of solitaire. Easy controls.
simple well designed game of Klondike.
Needs an ability for the player to reshuffle the cards. The deal comes up to many times with all black or all red cards to start with.
Good, clean design. Like the layout, menus, etc. Thanks to this app, I will continue to enjoy sucking at solitaire. Wait, who still has Hotmail?
